t: calc((1.5em + 3px) + 3px); padding-right: 2px;\"><div style=\"width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 6px; background: currentcolor; margin-top: 0.1em;\"></div></div><div style=\"flex: 1 1 0px; min-width: 1px; display: flex; flex-direction: column;\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\"List\" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding-top: 3px; padding-bottom: 3px; text-align: left;\">设备像素比 = 物理像素 / 设备独立像素</div></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"1fbeb517-1dd9-4bbf-a206-2783b9d07bc8\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-text-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: inherit; fill: inherit;\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"8cc8c483-57a6-420a-bc56-fe2f4b0e94ce\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-text-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: inherit; fill: inherit;\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">在dpr为 2 的设备下，1 个 css 像素，设备会使用 2 个物理像素去呈现它的宽和高，最终的结果也就是一个CSS像素，设备使用了4个物理像素去呈现。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"6d285cd4-22fc-457a-9382-c6909fda727c\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-text-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: inherit; fill: inherit;\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"8235eb5b-5ccb-45c5-be4d-02a9e060896d\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-sub_header-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 1.4em; margin-bottom: 1px; color: rgb(55, 53, 47);\"><div style=\"display: flex; width: 100%; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.5em; line-height: 1.3; color: inherit; fill: inherit;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\"Heading 2\" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">位图像素</div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"c9489402-efee-4ef0-bdf0-70b76eba46f5\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-divider-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div class=\"notion-cursor-default\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; pointer-events: auto; width: 100%; height: 13px; flex: 0 0 auto; color: rgb(228, 227, 226);\"><div style=\"width: 100%; height: 1px; visibility: visible; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.09);\"></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"e3e0f427-fba3-4025-b775-c1d9118a6bed\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-text-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: inherit; fill: inherit;\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">一个位图像素是栅格图像 (如：png,jpg,gif等) 最小的数据单元，每个位图像素都包含着一些自身的显示信息(显示位置，颜色值，透明度等)。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"05c24c52-a12b-4191-a3a3-d868c02b54a5\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-text-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: inherit; fill: inherit;\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">理论上，1个位像素对应1个物理像素，这是图片最完美的展示。这在dpr为1的屏幕设备下，没有问题；但在retina屏幕下，就会出现位图像素点不够，导致图片模糊的情况了，类似将小图片拉扯大，变模糊的效果。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"1eaa863b-6432-43ea-82a1-fd0d28abcf7d\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-image-block\" style=\"width: 600px; max-width: 800px; align-self: center; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\"><div><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div class=\"notion-cursor-default\" style=\"position: relative; overflow: hidden; flex-grow: 1;\"><div style=\"position: relative;\"><div style=\"height: 100%; width: 100%;\"><img src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F582f19ee-ebc6-4a39-b766-385fe5bdd1c7%2Fweitu.jpg?table=block&amp;id=1eaa863b-6432-43ea-82a1-fd0d28abcf7d&amp;width=1200&amp;cache=v2\" style=\"display: block; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 1px; width: 100%; pointer-events: auto;\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"b92f20c1-c7ab-4d72-8adf-35b5873f179d\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-text-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: inherit; fill: inherit;\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">由于单个位图像素不可再进行分割，所以设备只能就近取色，从而导致图片变得模糊。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"265c4ba6-fb75-40e7-ac77-f476c3871fcb\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-text-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: inherit; fill: inherit;\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px;\">所以，对于图片高清问题，通常的方案就是使用多倍图片。如在dpr为2的设备下，即对于200_300(css pixel)的图片，就需要提供 400\\_600 的图片(@2x)。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"eb8041f1-1886-4174-976d-34c0f15583ac\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-text-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div style=\"color: inherit; fill: inherit;\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"2d11b17b-8a1d-4367-893d-cb69407876f0\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-divider-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 1px;\"><div class=\"notion-cursor-default\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; pointer-events: auto; width: 100%; height: 13px; flex: 0 0 auto; color: rgb(228, 227, 226);\"><div style=\"width: 100%; height: 1px; visibility: visible; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.09);\"></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"f630a42b-8d0e-4036-9bc8-d3ffdc8b6728\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-callout-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 4px;\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div style=\"padding: 16px 16px 16px 12px; display: flex; width: 100%; border-radius: 3px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: transparent; background: rgba(235, 236, 237, 0.3);\"><div><div class=\"notion-record-icon\" role=\"button\" aria-disabled=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"user-select: none; transition: background 120ms ease-in 0s; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 24px; width: 24px; border-radius: 3px; flex-shrink: 0;\"><div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 24px; width: 24px;\"><div style=\"height: 16.8px; width: 16.8px; font-size: 16.8px; line-height: 1.1; margin-left: 0px; color: black;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, NotoColorEmoji, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Android Emoji&quot;, EmojiSymbols;\">💡</span></div></div></div></div><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\"Type something…\" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); margin-left: 8px;\">如果在普通屏幕下，对于200_300(css pixel)的图片，所对应的物理像素个数也就是200_300，假设使用2倍图片，其位图像素个数则是200*300*4；也就是会出现一个物理像素点对应4个位图像素点，在这个时候，设备对它的取色会通过一定的算法（显示结果就是一张只有原图像素总数4分之1）进行downsampling，肉眼看上去图片虽不会模糊，可以接受，但有时也会觉得图片缺少一些锐利度，或者是色差。</div></div></div></div><div data-block-id=\"d902e1e3-9429-424e-acbb-6d01bb76a791\" class=\"notion-selectable notion-text-block\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 608px; margin-top: 1px; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><div style=\"color: inherit; fill: inherit;\"><div style=\"display: flex;\"><div contenteditable=\"false\" spellcheck=\"true\" placeholder=\" \" data-root=\"true\" style=\"max-width: 100%; width: 100%; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; caret-color: rgb(55, 53, 47); padding: 3px 2px; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(55, 53, 47); -webkit-text-fill-color: rgba(55, 53, 47, 0.4);\"></div></div></div></div>","title":"pixel","category":["开发"],"tags":["css"],"publish_date":"2019-01-13","last_edited":"2020-04-05"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"fa12641c6c274f9d8144d0081253b80c"}}}